I think there is a "" thing in your command line.
change:
-DPYTHON_LIBRARIES="C:\Program Files\Anaconda3\libs\python35.lib
-Dtensorflow_BUILD_PYTHON_TESTS=ON"
to:
-DPYTHON_LIBRARIES="C:\Program Files\Anaconda3\libs\python35.lib"
"-Dtensorflow_BUILD_PYTHON_TESTS=ON"
